snippet.title: Rollerblade Racer (1993) [NES] Complete Playthrough
snippet.description:
Playthrough of Rollerblade Racer for NES.

▶️ Subscribe for more videos:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCCmsDPICSz4MfC07fhoNAw?sub_confirmation=1

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/dangermeat
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/danger_meat
Instagram: https://instagram.com/danger_meat
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@dangermeat

In Rollerblade Racer, the player's goal is to win the "super rollerblade challenge". This game was released for both the Nintendo Entertainment System and MS-DOS.

Players will first need to qualify by earning 5,000 points and completing several obstacle courses. These points are earned by performing stunts on suburbs, city streets, beaches, and parks. Additional points are earned by completing the course under the time limit. The main character is Kirk, who brags about purchasing a new pair of rollerskates.
